pos_mean_info_list.mean: 愉快地；有趣地；可享乐地
欣赏，享受；喜爱；使过得快活

word_group.brief_definition: 愉快经验；愉快的体验；愉悦体验
愉快的旅行；愉快的行程；令人愉悦的旅途

bilingual.source: Nothing is more enjoyable than playing tennis.
bilingual.target: 没有什么比打网球更令人愉快的了。

bilingual.source: I find reading books to be very enjoyable.
bilingual.target: 我发现读书是非常令人愉快的。

bilingual.source: We had an enjoyable time at the beach yesterday.
bilingual.target: 我们昨天在海滩度过了令人愉快的时光。

bilingual.source: Cooking can be an enjoyable activity if you have the right recipes.
bilingual.target: 如果你有合适的食谱，烹饪可以是一项令人愉快的活动。
高中生活可以是很愉快的。

bilingual.source: It's not always enjoyable for children to eat vegetables.
bilingual.target: 对于孩子们来说，总吃蔬菜并不是很愉快的。

bilingual.source: Music has long been considered to be an enjoyable pastime for many people.
bilingual.target: 对很多人来说，音乐一直被认为是令人愉快的消遣。

bilingual.source: We had a very enjoyable evening - thank you!
bilingual.target: 我们度过了一个非常愉快的夜晚——谢谢你！

bilingual.source: First, thanks for the most enjoyable weekend of my life.
bilingual.target: 首先，感谢这是我一生中最愉快的周末。
这是一次十分愉快的音乐会。

yingyinNormal.en: And the most enjoyable. Phoebe, say something.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也是最有意思的阶段哦，菲比，说点什么。

yingyinNormal.en: Of course you are. We have had many enjoyable talks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你当然是，我们的谈话可愉快了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, interesting. Isn't it? No, I mean what you find enjoyable.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真有意思。是吧？不，我指的是你觉得有趣的事情很有趣。

yingyinNormal.en: But it's enjoyable as hell to think about an undead ankylosaur going after a diplodocus.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但光想想一头不死的甲龙追杀一头梁龙，就够有意思了。

yingyinNormal.en: Cameron. Andrew. Enjoyable show. So did you direct? No, not this year. Ah, I didn't think so.
yingyinNormal.zh: 卡梅伦。安德鲁，表演挺有意思的，是你导演吗？今年不是。我我也觉得不是。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me. I've passed many an enjoyable evening playing this game. And I'm sure it's a lot more exciting when you play with other people.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜托，扭扭乐伴我度过了无数个美好的夜晚，而且我觉得和别人一起玩肯定更有趣。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: n. 享受；乐趣；享有；令人愉快的事物
adj. 令人愉快的；有乐趣的

word_family.mean: v. 享受的乐趣；喜爱；欣赏；享有；受益于；过得愉快；玩得开心；玩个痛快吧；尽情享受吧

sense_info_list.en: (of an activity or occasion) giving delight or pleasure

examination_example.sentence: It doesn't matter, so long as they're <highlight>enjoyable</highlight>, and not likely to have negative side effects, such as going on a wild spending spree.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 没关系，只要它们令人愉快，并且不太可能产生负面影响，例如无节制的消费。

examination_example.sentence: In fact, these commutes were reportedly more <highlight>enjoyable</highlight> compared with those without communication, which makes absolute sense, since human beings thrive off of social connections.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 事实上，据调查，与没有交流的通勤相比，这些有交流通勤更令人愉快，这是绝对有道理的，因为人类是在社会联系中成长起来的。

examination_example.sentence: Buying gifts or giving to charity is often more pleasurable than purchasing things for oneself, and luxuries are most <highlight>enjoyable</highlight> when they are consumed sparingly.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 购买礼物或捐赠给慈善机构通常比为自己购买物品更令人愉快，而奢侈品在节俭消费时最令人愉快。

examination_example.sentence: In an experiment, commuters who talked to nearby strangers found their commute more <highlight>enjoyable</highlight> than those who didn't.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在一项实验中，与附近的陌生人交谈的通勤者发现他们的通勤比那些不交谈的人更愉快。

examination_example.sentence: Choosing on behalf of someone else is an <highlight>enjoyable</highlight> task that doesn't suffer the same pitfalls.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为别人做选择是一项愉快的任务，不会陷入同样的陷阱。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: n. 享受；乐趣；享有；令人愉快的事物
adj. 令人愉快的；有乐趣的

word_family.mean: v. 享受的乐趣；喜爱；欣赏；享有；受益于；过得愉快；玩得开心；玩个痛快吧；尽情享受吧

sense_info_list.en: (of an activity or occasion) giving delight or pleasure

examination_example.sentence: A person who is unable to stimulate others' curiosity or make their life <highlight>enjoyable</highlight> may appear somewhat boring.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一个无法激发他人好奇心，或让他们的生活变得愉快的人可能会显得有些无聊。

examination_example.sentence: Ebike riders get the <highlight>enjoyable</highlight> part of cycling without the massive suffering of climbing huge hills.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 电动自行车的骑手可以享受骑车的乐趣，而且不用忍受爬山的巨大痛苦。

examination_example.sentence: When it is made fun and <highlight>enjoyable</highlight> to kids.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当它对孩子们来说变得有趣和愉快时。

高中生活可以是很愉快的。

examination_example.sentence: Music is not only <highlight>enjoyable</highlight>, it's also good for us in many other ways.
